review_title: Can be easy picked, drilled, shimmed and hammered off.
reviews:
Ignore the advertising. This lock, despite being touted as "pick-resistant", can be picked. And within seconds. Please, please just do a simple Youtube search of this and see. I don't enjoy talking trash about products or companies, but when a product is meant to protect 1000's of dollars, well, my attitude changes.

Moving on from that, the design is just weak. The steel is too thin and although it also claims "pry" resistance, im sure with a long enough breaker bar this thing would give in. In fact just hammering this thing would be enough I bet, because of how cheap and thin this metal appears.

The too long didn't read of this is: Cheap, thin, blantitly lying advertising. Easily picked, easily pried, easily drilled, and easily hammered off. A garbage product.
These will fit any standard game, cd, or dvd perfectly.
Toque fits bigger as some people have already said, this just appears to be Carhartts M.O with the majority of their clothing.
The best glasses cleaner I've ever used. Bought the three pack so I could have one in the car, one at work and one at home. Definitely worth the price.
